cs/Hydro/dev/typescript-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step0-为什么使用插件","content":"如果您参与过其他工程项目的开发，经常会遇到以下的痛点："},"466":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step0-为什么使用插件","content":"若修改前端源代码，需要重新编译打包前端，编译通常消耗大量的内存与时间，且编译完成后需要重启服务，用户侧资源缓存也会全部失效；"},"467":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step0-为什么使用插件","content":"修改代码后，尝试更新系统时，自己的修改被新版本覆盖，需要手动合并（或是直接丢失了更改），极大幅度增加维护成本；"},"468":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step0-为什么使用插件","content":"第三方社区出现的大量修改分支无法直接按需求进行组合/拼装，或是功能间存在冲突；"},"469":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step0-为什么使用插件","content":"基于以上痛点，Hydro 开创性的使用了插件系统，提供了一套完整的开发 API 供开发者使用，开发者基于提供的较稳定的 API 进行功能的编写，而无需过多关心内部实现，将功能拆分成多个最小的单元，允许用户根据需要进行自由组合，并在多个版本间达到一致性，同时提供热重载功能，提升开发效率。"},"470":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step0-为什么使用插件","content":"此教程将以编写剪贴板插件为例进行插件开发的说明。"},"471":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step1-初始化项目","content":"前置条件：NodeJS>=22"},"472":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step1-初始化项目","content":"使用 hydrooj addon create 快速在 /root/addon 下初始化一个插件或是在一个空文件夹中运行 yarn init 并按照提示填写相关信息。"},"473":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"有时我们希望使用本机的 IDE 编写插件上传到服务器（我们也推荐这么做，编辑器提供的代码补全可以很大程度简化开发流程），可以进行如下操作："},"474":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"在本机安装 NodeJS 和 yarn 。"},"475":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"参照步骤 1 使用 yarn init 创建一个项目。"},"476":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-19","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"使用 VSCode 打开插件文件夹。"},"477":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-20","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"使用 yarn add hydrooj -D 安装相关开发组件。"},"478":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-21","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"参照下文进行插件开发工作"},"479":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-22","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"将本地的文件夹上传至服务器，并使用 hydrooj addon add 插件绝对路径 启用上传的插件。"},"480":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-23","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step2-准备编写组件","content":"分析：剪贴板组件需要以下功能："},"481":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-24","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step2-准备编写组件","content":"与数据库交互来存储/检索相应文档。"},"482":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-25","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step2-准备编写组件","content":"提供 /paste/create 路由以创建新文档。"},"483":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-26","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step2-准备编写组件","content":"提供 /paste/show/:ID 来查看已创建的文档。"},"484":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-27","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step2-准备编写组件","content":"根据用户ID进行鉴权，允许将文档设置为私密以防止他人查看。"},"485":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-28","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step2-准备编写组件","content":"在路由中定义所有的函数应均为异步函数，支持的函数有：prepare, get, post, post[Operation], cleanup具体流程如下："},"486":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-29","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step2-准备编写组件","content":"如果在 this.response.template 指定模板则渲染，否则直接返回 this.response.body 中的内容。"},"487":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-30","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step2-准备编写组件","content":"在表单提交时的 operation 字段使用下划线，函数名使用驼峰命名。"},"488":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-31","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step2-准备编写组件","content":"如 <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"operation\" value=\"confirm_delete\"> 对应 postConfirmDelete 函数。"},"489":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-32","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step2-准备编写组件","content":"应当提供 apply 函数，并与定义的 Handler 一同挂载到 global.Hydro.handler[模块名] 位置。\napply 函数将在初始化阶段被调用。"},"490":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-33","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step4-template","content":"模板采用 nunjucks 语法。放置于 templates/ 文件夹下。会在请求结束时根据 response.template 的值选择模板，并使用 response.body 的值进行渲染，存入 response.body 中。若 response.template 为空或 request.headers['accept'] == 'application/json'，则跳过渲染步骤。"},"491":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-34","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step5-locale","content":"用于提供多国翻译。格式与 Hydro 的 locale 文件夹格式相同。"},"492":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-35","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step6-frontend","content":"在 frontend 文件夹下编写前端代码。命名符合 [a-zA-Z0-9_]+.page.tsx? 的文件会被自动作为入口点加载。paste 功能并不需要在前端有任何额外 js 驱动的交互，因此下方给出一个最基础的格式示例。"},"493":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","type":"page","content":"编译器和语言","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler"},"494":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#针对语言修改时间限制","content":"针对语言修改时间限制"},"495":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#cc-彩色编译错误信息","content":"C/C++ 彩色编译错误信息"},"496":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#进阶环境设置","content":"进阶环境设置"},"497":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#其他","content":"其他"},"498":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","content":"从 2022/8/12 开始，Hydro 为了避免宿主机环境变化对于评测的影响，对于 此后新安装的实例 默认使用 nix 管理环境。如果你是在这之前安装的 Hydro，请使用 apt 安装编译器后使用 pm2 restart hydro-sandbox 重启沙箱，并忽略本章节。"},"499":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","content":"以下是 nix 的简要操作说明："},"500":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","content":"使用 nix-env -iA nixpkgs.编译器名 安装新编译器，后重启沙箱 pm2 restart hydro-sandbox 生效。"},"501":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","content":"可以在 Nixos Search 中搜索你需要的编译器。以下是常用编译器的示例："},"502":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","content":"使用 nix-env -q 查看已安装的列表，后使用 nix-env -e 编译器名 即可删除对应的编译器。请注意不要误删 Hydro 基础组件，且操作完成后需要重启沙箱 pm2 restart hydro-sandbox 生效。"},"503":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","content":"部分语言（特指 Java 等）因为语言特性，编译需要使用较长的 CPU 时间，这在单核机器上尤为明显，\n可能需要花费数秒甚至数十秒才能完成 A+B 的编译。预期性能可以通过在主机上手动运行编译命令来测试："},"504":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","content":"同时部分编译器在可能时会尝试创建大量进程利用多核并行编译，请确保 judge 设置中 processLimit 项足够大，\n否则会因编译器无法创建进程导致编译失败。"},"505":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","content":"在编译器利用多核并行编译时，Hydro 会统计这些进程的 CPU 占用之和作为 CPU 资源限制，如出现编译超时错误，\n请调整系统设置中对应语言选项下的 compile_time_limit 项（单位 ms）。"},"506":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","content":"在使用 sh nix-env -iA nixpkgs.python3Packages.xxxxx 安装 python 包后，如果在沙箱环境中无法找到依赖。\n请参照 在沙箱中引入 Python 包 教程更新环境变量。"},"507":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#针对语言修改时间限制","content":"系统默认给 Java 和 Kotlin 提供两倍时限, 此行为可在语言设置中修改："},"508":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#cc-彩色编译错误信息","content":"确认您安装了支持彩色输出的编译器；"},"509":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#cc-彩色编译错误信息","content":"在系统设置中，将 C/C++ 编译命令后加上 -fdiagnostics-color=always"},"510":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#cc-彩色编译错误信息","content":"例："},"511":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#进阶环境设置","content":"如果你需要更加复杂的编译环境配置，我们建议使用编写单独的 nix 文件。"},"512":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#进阶环境设置","content":"复制以上文件，保存为 default.nix ，使用 nix-build 进行构建。构建后会产生一个 result 文件夹，记住该文件夹所在的路径。打开 ~/.hydro/mount.yaml 将其中 /root/.nix-profile 替换为编译出的 result 文件夹（切换到新的环境）之后保存并重启沙箱。"},"513":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-19","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#进阶环境设置","content":"后续若需更改环境配置，仅需要修改 default.nix 文件之后 nix-build 重新构建，再重启沙箱即可生效。构建过程中的缓存文件可以使用 nix-collect-garbage 进行清理。"},"514":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-20","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#进阶环境设置","content":"更详细的 nix 语言介绍，请参照 Nix Guide 和\nNix Manual。"},"515":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler-21","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/compiler#其他","content":"推荐阅读 HydroJudge 章节，了解更多关于评测机设置的详细信息。"},"516":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","type":"page","content":"部署 Hydro","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install"},"517":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"服务器选择"},"518":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install#部署","content":"部署"},"519":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install","content":"这里提供了几套方案帮助您建立自己的站点，请选择适合您的方案并继续。搭建过程中如果遇到问题欢迎 联系我们 提问。"},"520":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"不同服务商提供的 CPU 主频不同，下方数据仅供参考。最低服务器配置： CPU: 1核 内存: 2G。（约可允许 100 人使用）请尽量不要使用突发性能实例或共享型实例，这可能会导致评测时间计量不准确"},"521":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"CentOS 8 已于 2021-12-31 停止支持，后续不会为安全漏洞发布补丁，建议重装为其他操作系统。"},"522":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"兼容大部分 Linux 发行版，推荐使用 Debian 12 / Debian 11 / Ubuntu 22.04 （教程多，成功率高，上手简单），不支持 CentOS 及其各种变种："},"523":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"CentOS"},"524":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"Alibaba Cloud Linux"},"525":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"TencentOS"},"526":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"OpenCloudOS"},"527":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"如果你的机器内存较小（<=2GiB），请避免使用 Ubuntu 22.04，它会消耗较多的内存。建议使用 Debian 12 / Debian 11。如果你有 Linux 运维经验，Hydro 同样支持在 Alpine Linux 上运行，Alpine Linux 系统启动后仅占用 ~100M 内存，是在低配置服务器上运行的更优方案。"},"528":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"使用 腾讯云邀请链接(无折扣) 或 阿里云邀请链接(15%折扣) 下单购买服务器, 开发者可获约 15% 返现。"},"529":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"type: warn"},"530":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"已知天翼云不备案禁止使用 80/443 端口，若不熟悉相关流程建议购买时选择其他服务商。"},"531":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"type: warn"},"532":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"虚拟机用户请注意："},"533":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"Hydro 使用的数据库依赖于 CPU 的 avx 指令集以提高运行性能，大部分虚拟机软件默认没有启用 avx 指令集，请参照您使用的虚拟机软件说明。"},"534":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"虚拟机由于非独占 CPU，会导致评测时间计量精度降低。"},"535":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"由于虚拟机本身的数据保存机制，突然断电很容易导致数据库损坏无法读取，请务必定期备份数据库，有条件请购买 UPS 保证供电稳定。"},"536":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-19","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"Docker 用户请注意："},"537":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-20","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"使用安装脚本需要设置 USER 环境变量为 root。"},"538":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-21","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"需要使用 --privileged 参数启动容器，否则评测机无法运行。"},"539":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-22","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"开发组不对 docker 部署提供免费技术支持。"},"540":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-23","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"第三方面板（如宝塔）用户请注意："},"541":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-24","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"部分面板出现多次高危漏洞，为防止数据丢失，请不要在生产环境中使用！"},"542":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-25","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"开发者不对使用面板导致的任何问题负责。"},"543":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-26","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"开发组不对第三方面板部署提供免费技术支持。"},"544":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-27","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#服务器选择","content":"若您需要付费技术支持，可联系我们的企业微信。"},"545":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-28","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#部署","content":"Hydro 需要使用以下端口： 80, 443, 2019, 8888, 5050, 27017，请确保这些端口空闲。安装和安装后的所有操作均需要在 root 权限下进行！（sudo su 输入用户的密码, 或 su - 输入 root 账户的密码）。"},"546":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-29","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#部署","content":"运行下面的脚本，等待几分钟即可（建议复制防止敲错）："},"547":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-30","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#部署","content":"如果有特殊需求，安装脚本支持一些可选的高级选项，以此方式调用： . <(curl https://hydro.ac/setup.sh) --foo --bar"},"548":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-31","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#部署","content":"--no-caddy 不配置安装反向代理，只监听 127.0.0.1:8888 端口"},"549":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-32","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#部署","content":"--judge 仅作为独立评测机安装"},"550":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-33","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#部署","content":"阿里云/腾讯云/华为云等等用户安装后如果不能访问 请百度搜索 xx云 放行80端口脚本默认使用的为清华大学镜像。安装完成后，从 http://服务器ip/ 访问网页端，注册一个账号，之后在终端中使用"},"551":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-34","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#部署","content":"将首个注册用户设置为超级管理员。之后刷新页面，您应当能在上方导航栏看到控制面板入口。进入控制面板，右侧系统设置，验证管理员密码后按需修改配置，注意 Server BaseURL 一项需要填写访问网站用的完整的 URL，以 / 结尾。（重要，务必正确填写，样例：https://hydro.ac/）"},"552":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install-35","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install#部署","content":"系统安装后需要题库，可前往 https://hydro.ac/d/tk/p 免费专区进行下载，支持批量导入。\n至此，基础功能安装已全部完成，另，如果你的服务部署在内网，且希望外网的用户可以访问，可以百度搜索 “端口映射” 相关教程。"},"553":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy","type":"page","content":"反向代理 / SSL 配置","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy"},"554":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy#20221027-后使用脚本安装的实例已自动配置-caddy-反向代理请直接编辑位于-hydrocaddyfile-的配置文件","content":"2022/10/27 后使用脚本安装的实例已自动配置 Caddy 反向代理，请直接编辑位于 ~/.hydro/Caddyfile 的配置文件！"},"555":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy#20221027-后使用脚本安装的实例已自动配置-caddy-反向代理请直接编辑位于-hydrocaddyfile-的配置文件","content":"type: warn"},"556":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy#20221027-后使用脚本安装的实例已自动配置-caddy-反向代理请直接编辑位于-hydrocaddyfile-的配置文件","content":"若使用反向代理，请注意系统设置中的 server.xff 和 server.xhost 设置项需要填写正确（小写），分别对应反向代理所添加的标头名（通常为 x-forwarded-for 和 x-forwarded-host，部分反代工具会使用 x-real-ip 替代 x-forwarded-for）。server.xhost 设置项配置错误会导致用户无法登录等问题。(CsrfTokenError)server.xff 设置项配置错误会导致无法记录用户IP。"},"557":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy#20221027-后使用脚本安装的实例已自动配置-caddy-反向代理请直接编辑位于-hydrocaddyfile-的配置文件","content":"除一键安装脚本在安装 Caddy 后会自动配置设置项，其他工具请在使用工具前先配置好系统设置！否则将造成用户无法登录、无法记录用户IP等问题。"},"558":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy#20221027-后使用脚本安装的实例已自动配置-caddy-反向代理请直接编辑位于-hydrocaddyfile-的配置文件","content":"若您使用 Nginx，请注意配置 WebSocket 协议的反向代理，否则会导致评测状态无法自动刷新，在线 IDE 无法正常使用等问题。"},"559":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy#20221027-后使用脚本安装的实例已自动配置-caddy-反向代理请直接编辑位于-hydrocaddyfile-的配置文件","content":"Hydro 支持使用 Caddy, HaProxy 等工具进行反向代理，此处 提供了一些配置样例。"},"560":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/proxy#20221027-后使用脚本安装的实例已自动配置-caddy-反向代理请直接编辑位于-hydrocaddyfile-的配置文件","content":"Hydro 推荐您使用 Caddy。以下为样例 Caddyfile。\n提示：如果您的服务器位于国内，则需要进行备案后才能使用 80 和 443 端口。"},"561":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","type":"page","content":"在 RISC-V 架构设备上安装","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv"},"562":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#系统环境","content":"系统环境"},"563":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#初始化-nix-环境","content":"初始化 Nix 环境"},"564":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#构建-mongodb","content":"构建 MongoDB"},"565":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#安装各种组件并启动","content":"安装各种组件并启动"},"566":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#编译器语言兼容性","content":"编译器/语言兼容性"},"567":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#系统环境","content":"本文编写基于 Sipeed Lichee Pi 4A 16G, 使用 RevyOS 20250526_182059 固件，感谢 甲辰计划 提供的硬件支持，\n感谢 Anillc 和 NickCao 提供的帮助。"},"568":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#初始化-nix-环境","content":"为了节约生命，配置额外的 binary cache: https://cache.nichi.co https://nix-community.cachix.org\nnix-community.cachix.org-1:mB9FSh9qf2dCimDSUo8Zy7bkq5CX+/rkCWyvRCYg3Fs= hydra.nichi.co-0:P3nkYHhmcLR3eNJgOAnHDjmQLkfqheGyhZ6GLrUVHwk="},"569":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#构建-mongodb","content":"MongoDB 没有提供官方的 RISC-V 支持，因此我们需要自行编译 MongoDB （如果使用 MongoDB Atlas 则可跳过该步骤）。"},"570":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#构建-mongodb","content":"克隆 MongoDB 存储库："},"571":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#构建-mongodb","content":"下载 mozjs release:"},"572":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#构建-mongodb","content":"给同目录的 gen-config.sh 添加 RISC-V 支持："},"573":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#构建-mongodb","content":"运行 gen-config.sh 得到 platform/riscv64/linux 目录："},"574":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#构建-mongodb","content":"修改 MongoDB 的 platform/pause.h ，添加 RISC-V 支持："},"575":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#构建-mongodb","content":"将上述 patch 传入 nixpkgs："},"576":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#构建-mongodb","content":"以上修改可参照 Nixpkgs PR#430577"},"577":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv#构建-mongodb","content":"构建得到 MongoDB 7.0.22 的 RISC-V 版本，使用 nix copy 传入目标设备。"},"578":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/install/riscv-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/instal