708":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-22","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#准备","content":"如果不使用自动脚本，您需要按照如下方式手动安装沙箱服务：前往 criyle/go-judge 下载对应 cpu 架构的 go-judge。\ngo-judge 需要在后台运行并监听 127.0.0.1:5050 。如果系统使用的 cgroup 版本为 1 或者使用的为非 systemd init 的发行版，请以 root 权限运行。\n可使用 pm2 进行管理。"},"709":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-23","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为附加组件","content":"由于用附加组件安装的评测机与 Hydro 必须在同一台服务器上，每一个 Hydro 实例最多只能有一台评测机由附加组件安装。"},"710":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-24","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为附加组件","content":"在安装 Hydro 的机器上运行下面的指令安装 @hydrooj/hydrojudge："},"711":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-25","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为附加组件","content":"重启 Hydro 后 hydrojudge 即可正常运行。"},"712":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-26","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"该方法可以帮助您在任意服务器上部署评测机。"},"713":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-27","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"type: warn"},"714":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-28","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"我们推荐所有独立评测机使用相同配置机器并关闭内置评测机, 以保证评测结果的稳定性。系统设置中的评测机相关选项仅控制内置评测机, 独立评测机需要在 judge.yaml 中进行设置。"},"715":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-29","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"首先需要创建一个有 PRIV_JUDGE 权限的账户，具体方法参照 此处。（在部署 Hydro 的服务器上运行）"},"716":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-30","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"te