作为独立进程-1","content":"在 此处 的设置均可添加到此处。"},"726":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-40","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#修改编译选项添加新语言支持","content":"在 控制面板>系统设置 中修改 hydrooj.langs 配置项(对所有连接到该服务器的评测机生效)或在 ~/.config/hydro/langs.yaml 中配置(对单个独立评测机生效, 不推荐)。"},"727":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-41","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#修改编译选项添加新语言支持","content":"文件格式参照 此处 。"},"728":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-42","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#修改编译选项添加新语言支持","content":"如果您添加了新的语言，您还需要前往 控制面板>系统设置 中修改 Language Highlight ID 与 Monaco language modes。分别表示选择对应的语言后的高亮设置（基于 PrismJS）和 Monaco 编辑器语法规则设置。"},"729":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-43","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#修改编译选项添加新语言支持","content":"修改完后请重启 Hydro 和 hydrojudge 。"},"730":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-44","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#修改编译选项添加新语言支持","content":"在 编译器和语言 章节可查看更多信息。"},"731":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-45","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#调试沙箱环境","content":"如果需要调试沙箱内的编译或者运行错误，可以使用 hydrojudge terminal 来打开评测交互终端。该终端运行于与评测环境相同的独立沙箱内。"},"732":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-46","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#清除数据缓存","content":"若需要清除评测数据缓存，可以使用 hydrojudge cache prune 清除 30 天之内未使用的测试数据，需指定天数可添加参数 --duration=x 清除 x 天数据。"},"733":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-47","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#清除数据缓存","content":"若需清除所有缓存数据，可以使用 hydrojudge cache clean 命令。"},"734":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins