s/vjudge#codeforces","content":"将如下配置添加至 langs 设置末尾："},"900":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge#codeforces","content":"之后再重启 Hydro 即可。"},"901":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"page","content":"使用内容分发网络","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn"},"902":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#资源-cdn","content":"资源 CDN"},"903":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"全站 CDN"},"904":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","content":"如您希望改善 Hydro 的访问质量，在您的服务器带宽较小的情况下，您可以考虑使用内容分发网络，即 CDN ，通常情况下您仅需设置资源 CDN 即可大幅度改善访问质量，关于如何使用内容分发网络和使用中的任何问题请联系各大云厂商。"},"905":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#资源-cdn","content":"创建并配置好资源 CDN ，在控制面板中将 server.cdn 设置项修改为 CDN 域名。（如 https://cdn.hydro.ac/，以 / 结尾）。"},"906":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#资源-cdn","content":"CDN 的回源地址配置为源站，缓存时间可按需设置（推荐一个星期或更久）并放行 CORS 和 Referer（可能名为防盗链），设置允许空 Referer 请求。"},"907":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"如果您预算充足，可以使用全站 CDN。"},"908":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"type: warn"},"909":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"全站 CDN 配置较为繁琐，如您没有相关使用经验请仅建立并配置资源 CDN ，配置资源 CDN 在大部分情况下即可大幅度改善访问质量。\n因各服务商全站 CDN 配置方法不同，配置过程不同，需要配置的内容较多，以下仅为参考配置，如果有任何问题建议先查阅云服务商文档及咨询云服务商工程师。"},"910":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"type: warn"},"911":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"配置全站 CDN 时需要启用 CDN 的 WebSocket 支持（不同服务商开启方式可能不同，且可能额外收费），否则会导致评测状态无法自动更新/IDE无法使用等等问题。请确认仅缓存了资源文件！否则可能导致用户登录状态混乱。"},"912":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"缓存设置可以参考以下设置："},"913":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"类型"},"914":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"内容"},"915":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"缓存行为"},"916":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"全部文件"},"917":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"全部文件"},"918":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"遵循源站"},"919":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"文件后缀"},"920":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"jpg,js,png,css,gif"},"921":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-19","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/syst